<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘看着仙女。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？我可以去参加舞会吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。你跑到花园里去给我拿个南瓜来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“南瓜？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘朝花园跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她找到一个漂亮的南瓜跑了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给您！”灰姑娘把南瓜放在仙女面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女用魔杖轻轻地敲了敲南瓜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>南瓜变成了一辆黄金马车！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来，我们需要一些马。”仙女说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能找到一些老鼠！”灰姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女数了数。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三，四。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！老鼠变成了一队马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”仙女看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁来赶黄金马车呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地下室里有老鼠。”灰姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”仙女回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我拿一只来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>转眼间，一个长着胡子的马夫站在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两只蜥蜴成了年轻的仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的马车准备好了，宝贝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是......”灰姑娘指着自己的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女用魔杖轻轻地碰了她一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘的破衣服不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，她穿着一件漂亮的礼服，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面镶着闪闪发光的珠宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，她的脚上......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘穿着世上最漂亮的水晶鞋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她上了马车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，仙女！我要去参加舞会了！”</Text>
